      "temperature_sensitive_ideal_10_29_c_ab": "Temperature-sensitive: ideal 10–29°C. Above 32°C can kill queens and brood. Works year-round but risky in peak summer heat. Queen is briefly caged or may be superseded.",
      "thymol_apiguard": "Thymol (Apiguard)",
