      "mechanical_no_chemicals_harmless_to_be": "Mechanical, no chemicals. Harmless to bees. Only affects ~5–15% of mites (those on adult bees, not in brood). Effective as monitoring + supplemental control, not as sole treatment.",
      "drone_brood_removal": "Drone Brood Removal",
